caption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%202024%20election%20is%20already%20the%20most%20litigated%20in%20US%20history.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ERepublicans%20and%20Democrats%20have%20been%20involved%20in%20a%20bevy%20of%20pre-election%20lawsuits.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ETrump%20allies%20are%20waging%20most%20of%20the%20legal%20battles%2C%20and%20experts%20expect%20more%20to%20come%20postelection.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-long-will-it-take-to-call-us-presidential-election-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2024%20US%20presidential%20election%3C%2Fa%3E%20just%20days%20away%2C%20the%20high-stakes%20race%20is%20already%20the%20most%20litigated%20in%20modern%20American%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20months%2C%20Republican%20allies%20of%20former%20President%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-harris-presidency-impact-ai-artificial-intelligence-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDonald%20Trump%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Democratic%20allies%20of%20Vice%20President%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkamala-harris-closing-argument-washington-dc-speech-policty-economy-trump-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKamala%20Harris%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20have%20been%20involved%20in%20a%20barrage%20of%20pre-election%20lawsuits%2C%20with%20Republicans%20waging%20the%20majority%20of%20the%20legal%20challenges%20in%20key%20battleground%20ground%20states.%20And%20while%20preelection%20litigation%20might%20not%20feel%20like%20a%20fundamental%20part%20of%20democratic%20presidential%20elections%20in%20the%20US%2C%20the%202024%20cycle%20has%20proved%20it%20to%20be%20a%20keystone%20political%20strategy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BProbably%20the%20most%20discouraging%20part%20of%20this%20whole%20litigation%20experiment%20is%20that%20it%20has%20little%20or%20no%20connection%20to%20democracy%20and%20credible%20elections%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20John%20Har