s%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fce8144v9pveo%5C%22%3EBBC%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20Sarco%20pod%2C%20designed%20by%20Dr%20Philip%20Nitschke%2C%20founder%20of%20Exit%20International%2C%20is%20intended%20to%20allow%20terminally%20ill%20patients%20to%20end%20their%20lives.%20Operated%20by%20the%20Swiss%20assisted-dying%20group%20The%20Last%20Resort%2C%20the%20pod%20requires%20the%20user%20to%20press%20an%20internal%20button%2C%20which%20releases%20nitrogen%20gas%2C%20causing%20them%20to%20fall%20asleep%20and%20then%20die%20peacefully%20within%20minutes%20due%20to%20oxygen%20deprivation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ESwiss%20police%20were%20notified%20and%20later%20found%20the%20woman's%20body%20inside%20the%20pod.%20Dr%20Florian%20Willet%2C%20president%20of%20The%20Last%20Resort%2C%20was%20reportedly%20the%20only%20person%20present%20at%20the%20time%20of%20her%20death%20and%20remains%20in%20custody.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ESwiss%20Chief%20Prosecutor%20Peter%20Sticher%2C%20leading%20the%20investigation%2C%20has%20suggested%20that%20the%20woman's%20death%20may%20not%20have%20been%20as%20intended%2C%20indicating%20the%20possibility%20of%20%E2%80%9Cintentional%20homicide%2C%E2%80%9D%20according%20to%20de%20Volkskrant.%20The%20report%20highlights%20that%20strangulation%20could%20be%20a%20factor%2C%20raising%20questions%20about%20the%20circumstances%20of%20her%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20report%20notes%20that%20the%20pod%20was%20opened%20and%20closed%20several%20times%20before%20the%20procedure%20began%20to%20verify%20its%20seal.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EA%20forensic%20expert%20testified%20in%20court%20that%20the%20woman%20had%20severe%20injuries%20to%20her%20neck%2C%20which%20has%20further%20fuelled%20suspicion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20incident%20was%20reportedly%20recorded%20by%20two%20surveillance%20cameras%20%E2%80%93%20one%20inside%20the%20pod%2C%20focused%20on%20the%20control%20button%2C%20and%20another%20mounted%20on%20a%20nearby%20tree.%20These%20cameras%20were%20motion-activated%20and%20not%20set%20to%20record%20continuously.%20De%20Volkskrant%2C%20who%20reviewed%20the%20footage%2C%20observed%20that%20the%20internal%20camera%20activated%20twice%20in%20quick%20succession%20around%20two%20minutes%20after%20the%20woman%20pressed%20the%20button%2C%20although%20the%20camera%20angle%20did%20not%20clearly%20show%20what%20occurred.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20the%20report%2C%20Dr%20Willet%20later%20informed%20police%20that%20about%20two%20and%20a%20half%20minutes%20into%20the%20procedure%2C%20the%20woman's%20body%20appeared%20to%20cramp%20strongly%20%E2%80%93%20a%20reaction%20he%20described%20as%20typical%20in%20deaths%20involving%20nitrogen.%20Six%20and%20a%20half%20minutes%20after%20the%20woman%20initiated%20the%20process%2C%20the%20pod's%20iPad%20reportedly%20emitted%20a%20loud%20alarm%2C%20prompting%20Dr%20Willet%2C%20who%20was%20on%20a%20call%20with%20Dr%20Philip%20Nitschke%2C%20to%20say%2C%20%E2%80%9CShe's%20still%20alive%2C%20Philip.%E2%80%9D%20The%20alarm%20ceased%20after%20some%20time%2C%20and%20roughly%2030%20minutes%20after%20pressing%20the%20button%2C%20Dr%20Willet%20reportedly%20confirmed%2C%20%E2%80%9CShe%20really%20looks%20dead.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20Swiss%20authorities%20have%20yet%20to%20confirm%20these%20findings%20publicly%2C%20and%20the%20prosecutor's%20office%20has%20refrained%20from%20making%20an%20official%20statement%20on%20the%20ongoing%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ESwiss%20law%20prohibits%20assisted%20suicide%20if%20external%20assistance%20is%20involved%20or%20if%20those%20assisting%20have%20any%20%E2%80%9Cself-serving%20motive.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ctable%3E%3Cthead%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Cth%20colspan%3D%5C%222%5C%22%3EHelplines%3C%2Fth