nsider.com%2Felon-musk-tesla-twitter-wall-street-disappointment-self-driving-taxi-2024-10%3Futm_source%3Dtwitter%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_campaign%3Dbusiness-sf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EElon%20Musk%20says%20all%20kinds%20of%20things%20all%20the%20time%3C%2Fa%3E.%20And%20unlike%20his%20competitors%2C%20he%20doesn't%20report%20his%20numbers%20to%20the%20US%20Securities%20and%20Exchange%20Commission.%20So%2C%20maybe%20take%20that%20one%20with%20a%20grain%20of%20salt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20any%20case%2C%20Meta%20says%20Threads%20is%20growing%20very%2C%20very%20fast%20and%20has%20been%20adding%20a%20million%20sign-ups%20a%20day.%20Back%20in%20April%2C%20Meta%20said%20Threads%20had%20150%20million%20monthly%20users.%20Which%20means%20it%20has%20grown%2083%25%20in%20half%20a%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20all%20of%20that%20is%20hard%20to%20square%20with%20my%20experience%20on%20Threads.%20I'm%20there%20quite%20a%20bit%2C%20posting%20and%20reading%20for%20fun%20and%20for%20work.%20And%20it%20doesn't%20%3Cem%3Eseem%3C%2Fem%3E%20like%20the%20place%20has%20nearly%20doubled%20recently.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20isn't%20a%20metrics-based%20argument%20%E2%80%94%20I'm%20not%20tracking%20the%20engagement%20for%20my%20posts%20in%20any%20serious%20way.%20Just%20a%20vibes%20thing.%20When%20Threads%20launched%20in%20July%202023%2C%20it%20definitely%20felt%20empty%2C%20especially%20compared%20to%20what%20was%20then%20still%20called%20Twitter.%20It's%20picked%20up%20since%20then.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20certainly%20doesn't%20%3Cem%3Eseem%3C%2Fem%3E%20anything%20close%20to%20what%20Twitter%20was%20like%20back%20in%202019%2C%20back%20when%20lots%20of%20people%20were%20calling%20it%20a%20hellsite%20and%20also%20checking%20it%20every%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20giggles%2C%20I%20did%20the%20classic%20lazy%20reporter%20gambit%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.threads.net%2F%40pkafka%2Fpost%2FDBw8SM1vVs9%3Fxmt%3DAQGzyjSmOAZYKh3IpKeRX14NMdblVMtkbhVVMJ0pY_PGUw%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Easked%20people%20on%20Threads%20if%20it%20felt%20like%20the%20place%20has%20gotten%20a%20lot%20more%20full%20recently%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20results%20seem%20split.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpecial%20shout%20out%20to%20sami3456567%2C%20whose%20bio%20says%20he's%20no%20fan%20of%20%26quot%3Bincels%2C%20present%20%26amp%3B%20future%20cat%20ladies%2C%20anything%20remotely%20French.%26quot%3B%20You'll%20always%20have%20a%20place%20in%20social%20media%2C%20sami.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221290%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Screengrab%20from%20Peter%20Kafka%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67256d4e01ea6d83dee5c33e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22904%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EScreengrab%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20reason%20I%20may%20not%20be%20noticing%20that%20Threads%20seems%20more%20crowded%20is%20that%20some%20of%20that%20growth%20is%20coming%20from%20people%20who%20are%20unlikely%20to%20be%20posting%20in%20English%3A%20Meta%20says%20a%20bunch%20of%20its%20recent%20users%20have%20been%20coming%20from%20Japan%20and%20Taiwan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20most%20obvious%20reason%20Threads%20can%20grow%20so%20fast%20is%20that%20Meta%20surfaces%20Threads%20posts%20in%20Instagram%2C%20which%20%3Cem%3Edoes%3C%2Fem%3E%20have%20gazillions%20of%20users.%20Some%20of%20them%20click%20on%20Threads%20posts%20they%20see%20there%2C%20and%20become%20Threads%20users%20that%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20you%20can%20definitely%20see%2C%20or%20at%20least%20%3Cem%3Efeel%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20presence%20of%20Instagram%20users%20who%20are%20logging%20into%20Threads.%20They're%20the%20people%20who%20seem%20to%20have%20wandered%20into%20the%20bar%20not%20completely%20knowing%20why%20they're%20there%20or%20what%20they're%20supposed%20to%20do%2C%20and%20they%20are%20prime%20targets%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthreads-meta-engagement-rage-bait-viral-katie-notopoulos-i-tried-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emy%20colleague%20Katie%20Notopoulos%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20it's%20entirely%20possible%20that%20if%20I%20used%20Threads%20differently%2C%20and%20wasn't%20trying%20to%20stubbornly%20use%20it%20as%20a%20text-centric%2C%20news-centric%20Twitter%20replacement%2C%20I%20might%20see%20more%20of%20those%20fresh-off-the-boat%20Instagram%20users.%20Or%20more%20users%2C%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20I%20still%20want%20a%20version%20of%20Twitter%20like%20the%20one%20I%20spent%20way%20too%20much%20time%20on%2C%20especially%20in%20its%20early%20days%2C%20when%20it%20was%20way%20too%20easy%20to%20be%20naive%20about%20how%20people%20might%20behave%20when%20you%20connected%20a%20lot%20of%20them%20on%20the%20internet%20without%20a%20lot%20of%20ground%20rules.%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpodcasts.apple.com%2Fus%2Fpodcast%2Fland-of-the-giants-what-we-all-got-wrong-about-twitter%2Fid1080467174%3Fi%3D1000633427694%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EI%20made%20a%20whole%20podcast%20series%20about%20that%20era%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20RIP.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThreads%20doesn't%20seem%20like%20it's%20ever%20going%20to%20be%20that%2C%20and%20Meta%20doesn't%20seem%20very%20interested%20in%20trying%20to%20make%20that.%20Which%20makes%20some%20sense%20since%20Meta%20is%20in%20the%20business%20of%20making%20money%2C%20and%20even%20on%20its%20best%20days%2C%20Twitter%20wasn't%20very%20good%20at%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20let%20me%20add%20this%20request%20to%20Instagram%2FThreads%20boss%20Adam%20Mosseri's%20very%20long%20to-do%20list%3A%20If%20there%20are%20this%20many%20people%20hanging%20out%20on%20Threads%2C%20can%20you%20help%20me%20find%20them%3F%20Thanks%20in%20advance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthreads-users-how-many-meta-twitter-instagram-2024-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730