%3A%22Four%20children%2C%20aged%202%20to%207%2C%20tragically%20died%20from%20suffocation%20inside%20a%20locked%20car%20in%20Randhiya%20village%2C%20Gujarat.%20Left%20unattended%20while%20their%20parents%20worked%20at%20a%20nearby%20farm%2C%20the%20children%20entered%20the%20car%20owner's%20vehicle%20and%20became%20trapped.%20Their%20bodies%20were%20discovered%20later%20that%20evening%2C%20leading%20to%20an%20investigation%20by%20the%20Amreli%20police.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20CITY%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BWhat%20Steps%20Taken%3F%26quot%3B%20Court%20Pulls%20Up%20Delhi%20Government%2C%20Top%20Cop%20Over%20Cracker%20Ban%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Monday%20demanded%20an%20%26quot%3Bimmediate%26quot%3B%20response%20from%20the%20Delhi%20government%20and%20police%20to%20the%20ban%20-%20which%20seems%20to%20exist%20on%20paper%20only%20-%20against%20firecrackers%20during%20Diwali%2C%20a%20ban%20that%20is%20announced%2C%20and%20ignored%2C%20every%20year%2C%20resulting%20in%20a%20suffocating%20blanket%20of%20toxic%20air%20smothering%20the%20national%20capital%20and%20surrounding%20regions%20for%20days%20after%20the%20festival%20is%20celebrated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20issued%20notice%20to%20the%20Delhi%20government%2C%20led%20by%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%2C%20and%20the%20police%2C%20which%20reports%20to%20the%20Union%20Home%20Minister%2C%20to%20explain%20steps%20taken%20to%20implement%20and%20enforce%20the%20ban%20this%20year%2C%20as%20also%20measures%20for%20the%20next%20to%20%26quot%3Benforce%20a%20complete%20ban%26quot%3B%20on%20firecrackers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20widespread%20news%20reports%20the%20ban%20on%20firecrackers%20(in%20Delhi%20NCR)%20was%20not%20implemented%20at%20all...%20this%20was%20supposed%20to%20be%20an%20important%20measure%20to%20reduce%20pollution%2C%26quot%3B%20Justice%20Abhay%20S%20Oka%20and%20Justice%20Augustine%20George%20Masih%20said%20this%20afternoon%2C%20as%20they%20continued%20a%20long-running%20(and%20annual)%20hearing%20into%20the%20air%20quality%20crisis%20that%20consumes%20Delhi%20every%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20is%20the%20order%20(on%20banning%20of%20firecrackers)%20...%20how%20is%20it%20being%20implemented...%20something%20has%20to%20be%20worked%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20asked%20the%20Delhi%20government%2C%20and%20tasked%20it%20with%20creating%20a%20mechanism%20%26quot%3Bat%20least%20for%20next%20year%26quot%3B%20to%20ensure%20Delhi%20doesn't%20choke%20on%20aerial%20pollutants%20in%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%20morning%20the%20air%20quality%20index%2C%20or%20AQI%2C%20in%20Delhi%20plummeted%20across%20the%20city%2C%20even%20four%20days%20after%20Diwali%2C%20to%20the%20'severe'%20category.%20The%20AQI%20reading%20fell%20past%20the%20400-mark%20(on%20a%20scale%20of%20500)%20in%20many%20neighbourhoods%2C%20including%20Anand%20Vihar%2C%20Rohini%2C%20Ashok%20Vihar%2C%20and%20Vivek%20Vihar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20the%20more%20affluent%20areas%20-%20such%20as%20Lodi%20Road%20-%20were%20not%20spared%20the%20toxic%20blanket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2024-hour%20average%20AQI%2C%20as%20of%207am%2C%20was%20373%20-%20almost%20as%20bad%20as%20it%20was%20Sunday%2C%20when%20it%20hit%20a%20season-worst%20of%20382.%20That%20these%20readings%20came%20despite%20a%20decrease%20-%20by%2015%20per%20cent%20-%20in%20the%20contribution%20of%20farm%20fires%20to%20toxic%20pollutants%20in%20the%20air%20only%20underlines%20the%20problem%20at%20hand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20situation%20in%20the%20NCR%20region%20also%20remained%20concerning%2C%20with%20Noida%20at%20305%2C%20Ghaziabad%20at%20295%2C%20and%20Gurugram%20at%20276.%20High%20AQI%20levels%20were%20also%20recorded%20in%20nearby%20states%2C%20including%20Haryana's%20Hisar%20(372)%2C%20and%20Sriganganagar%20(397)%20and%20Bharatpur%20(320)%