trators%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BThe%20JMM-RJD-Congress%20government%20has%20taken%20appeasement%20to%20its%20peak.%20These%20parties%20are%20destroying%20the%20state's%20social%20harmony.%20They%20are%20supporters%20of%20infiltrators.%20To%20get%20votes%20of%20Bangladesh%20infiltrators%2C%20they%20are%20getting%20them%20settled%20across%20Jharkhand%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20schools%20disallow%20Saraswati%20Vandana%2C%20you%20can%20imagine%20how%20big%20the%20danger%20is.%20When%20there%20is%20stone-pelting%20during%20festivals%2C%20Maa%20Durga%20is%20stopped%20and%20curfew%20is%20imposed%2C%20you%20know%20how%20dangerous%20it%20is.%20When%20the%20issue%20of%20infiltration%20goes%20to%20court%20and%20the%20administration%20denies%2C%20it%20become%20clear%20that%20the%20government%20machinery%20has%20been%20infiltrated.%20They%20are%20taking%20your%20roti%2C%20beti%20and%20maati%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said.%20He%20was%20referring%20to%20allegations%20that%20a%20Muslim%20teacher%20stopped%20prayers%20to%20Goddess%20Saraswati%20at%20a%20school%20in%20Jharkhand's%20Giridih.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20the%20bad%20policies%20of%20JMM%2C%20Congress%20and%20RJD%20continue%2C%20the%20adivasi%20society%20in%20Jharkhand%20will%20shrink.%20So%2C%20use%20your%20vote%20to%20uproot%20this%20infiltrator%20coalition%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20Jharkhand's%20swift%20development%20is%20possible%20only%20if%20it%20has%20a%20government%20that%20expedites%20the%20implementation%20of%20central%20schemes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20direct%20offensive%20targeting%20Hemant%20Soren%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20referred%20to%20the%20JMM's%20decision%20to%20replace%20Champai%20Soren%20as%20Chief%20Minister%20after%20Hemant%20Soren%20was%20granted%20bail%20in%20a%20money%20laundering%20case.%20Champai%20Soren%2C%20one%20a%20trusted%20lieutenant%20of%20Hemant%20Soren%2C%20is%20now%20with%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20did%20they%20do%20with%20Champai%20Soren%20ji!%20They%20left%20no%20stone%20unturned%20in%20humiliating%20an%20adivasi%20son.%20How%20will%20they%20care%20for%20you%20when%20nothing%20matters%20to%20them%20more%20than%20family.%20I%20would%20ask%20every%20young%20man%20of%20Jharkhand%2C%20it%20is%20necessary%20to%20teach%20a%20lesson%20to%20such%20selfish%20parties%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20have%20a%20family%2C%20you%20are%20my%20family.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccusing%20the%20ruling%20coalition%20of%20corruption%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BCorruption%20hollows%20out%20the%20country%20like%20termites.%20It%20destroys%20the%20poor%2C%20Dalits%2C%20people%20from%20backward%20classes%20and%20tribals.%20Jharkhand%20has%20seen%20for%20five%20years%20the%20corruption%20of%20the%20JMM-Congress-RJD%20government.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20then%20referred%20to%20the%20massive%20cash%20haul%20from%20the%20home%20of%20Congress's%20former%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20Dhiraj%20Sahu%20last%20year.%20%26quot%3BMountains%20of%20cash%20are%20recovered%20from%20the%20home%20of%20Congress's%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP.%20I%20have%20never%20seen%20such%20mountains.%20I%20saw%20them%20on%20TV.%20Machines%20got%20tired%20during%20the%20counting%2C%20Didn't%20this%20money%20belong%20to%20Jharkhand%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20the%20Congress%20had%20said%20Mr%20Sahu%20is%20from%20a%20business%20family%20and%20the%20cash%20recovered%20was%20in%20no%20way%20linked%20to%20the%20party%20or%20the%20state%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730709360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Ftfn1lk6o_pm-modi-jharkhand_625x300_04_November_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F2024-jharkhand-election-pm-narendra-modi-pms-infiltrator-jab-at-hemant-sorens-party-congress-in-jharkhand-rally-6940229%22%