20the%20union%20government's%20'One%20Nation%2C%20One%20Election'%20proposal.%20There%20was%20also%20a%20resolution%20against%20Mr%20Stalin's%20government%20for%20its%20handling%20of%20the%20southern%20state's%20finances.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVijay's%20TVK%20has%20ruffled%20the%20feathers%20of%20both%20the%20DMK%20and%20its%20long-time%20rival%2C%20the%20All%20India%20Anna%20Dravida%20Munnetra%20Kazhagam%2C%20since%20it%20was%20registered%20as%20a%20political%20party%20on%20September%208.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcopyist-cocktail-ideology-dmk-aiadmk-mock-actor-politician-vijays-party-6892645%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BCopyist%26quot%3B%2C%20%26quot%3BCocktail%20Ideology%26quot%3B%3A%20DMK%2C%20AIADMK%20Mock%20Actor-Politician%20Vijay%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20DMK%20and%20AIADMK%2C%20and%20the%20Dravidian%20ideology%20at%20their%20core%2C%20dominate%20Tamil%20Nadu%20politics%2C%20making%20it%20next%20to%20impossible%20for%20national%20parties%20like%20the%20BJP%20and%20Congress%20to%20make%20their%20mark.%20The%20TVK%20will%20hope%20to%20break%20that%20stranglehold%20with%20help%20from%20the%20actor's%20immense%20popularity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPerhaps%20predictably%2C%20the%20TVK%20has%20not%20been%20received%20favourably%20by%20the%20DMK%20or%20AIADMK.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20Vijay%20accused%20the%20DMK%2C%20and%20hit%20out%20at%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20his%20family's%20legacy%2C%20of%20having%20cheated%20the%20people%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu%20%26quot%3Bin%20the%20name%20of%20the%20Dravidian%20model%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20week%20the%20ruling%20party%20dismissed%20the%20newcomer's%20political%20ideology%20as%20having%20been%20copied%20from%20its%20books%2C%20while%20the%20opposition%20party%20called%20it%20a%20%26quot%3Bcocktail%26quot%3B%20of%20various%20political%20positions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%