ollow%2Cnoindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnypost.com%2F2024%2F11%2F03%2Fus-news%2Ffloridas-killer-clown-sheila-keen-warren-released-from-prison%2F%5C%22%3ENew%20York%20Post%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGreg%20Rosenfeld%2C%20Keen-Warren's%20attorney%2C%20said%20she%20accepted%20the%20plea%20deal%20only%20because%20it%20meant%20she%20could%20be%20released%20soon%2C%20avoiding%20the%20risk%20of%20a%20life%20sentence.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20thrilled%20that%20Ms%20Keen-Warren%20has%20been%20released%20from%20prison%20and%20is%20returning%20to%20her%20family.%20As%20we've%20stated%20from%20the%20beginning%2C%20she%20did%20not%20commit%20this%20crime%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mr%20Rosenfeld%20reportedly%20said%20in%20a%20message.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20dates%20back%20to%201990%20when%20Marlene%20Warren%20was%20shot%20in%20her%20home%20by%20an%20assailant%20dressed%20as%20a%20clown.%20According%20to%20Ms%20Warren's%20son%2C%20Joseph%20Ahrens%2C%20he%20and%20his%20friends%20were%20present%20when%20a%20clown%20appeared%20at%20their%20door%20bearing%20balloons.%20When%20Ms%20Warren%C2%A0opened%20the%20door%2C%20the%20clown%20handed%20her%20the%20balloons%20and%2C%20after%20she%20commented%2C%20%E2%80%9CHow%20nice%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20clown%20pulled%20out%20a%20gun%20and%20shot%20her%20in%20the%20face%20before%20fleeing%20the%20scene.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDetectives%20had%20suspected%20Keen-Warren%20for%20years%2C%20though%20it%20wasn't%20until%202017%20that%20she%20was%20arrested%2C%20with%20authorities%20attributing%20the%20delay%20to%20advancements%20in%20DNA%20technology%20that%20allegedly%20linked%20her%20to%20the%20crime.%20But%20Mr%20Rosenfeld%2C%20Keen-Warren's%20attorney%2C%20maintained%20that%20this%20evidence%20was%20unreliable.%C2%A0He%20highlighted%20issues%20with%20the%20DNA%20evidence%2C%20claiming%20it%20contained%20both%20male%20and%20female%20genes%20and%20that%20one%20of%20the%20samples%20was%20common%20enough%20that%20it%20could%20have%20matched%20many