sments%20extend%20beyond%20nutritional%20profiles.%20Their%20algorithm%20evaluates%20several%20factors%3A%2045%25%20is%20based%20on%20the%20nutritional%20profile%2C%2045%25%20on%20the%20health%20impact%20of%20ingredients%2C%20and%2010%25%20on%20the%20manufacturing%20process.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20adhere%20to%20ICMR%20and%20NIN%20standards%20set%20by%20dietitians%20and%20nutritionists%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ravi%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20algorithm%20interprets%20product%20images%2C%20extracting%20and%20manually%20verifying%20information%20before%20assigning%20a%20health%20rating.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20even%20penalise%20products%20for%20adding%20known%20harmful%20additives%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr%20Aman%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnhealthy%20diets%2C%20alongside%20physical%20inactivity%2C%20tobacco%20and%20alcohol%20use%2C%20and%20air%20pollution%2C%20remain%20major%20contributors%20to%20non-communicable%20diseases%20(NCDs).%20A%20report%20by%20the%20Indian%20Council%20of%20Medical%20Research%20(ICMR)%20reveals%20that%20the%20proportion%20of%20deaths%20from%20non-communicable%20diseases%20(NCDs)%20in%20India%20rose%20significantly%2C%20from%2037.9%25%20in%201990%20to%2061.8%25%20in%202016%2C%20with%20cardiovascular%20diseases%2C%20chronic%20respiratory%20diseases%2C%20cancers%2C%20and%20diabetes%20being%20the%20leading%20causes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229669016977%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20these%20rising%20concerns%20that%20TruthIn%20hopes%20to%20address.%C2%A0%20%E2%80%9CIf%20we%20talk%20about%20potato%20chips%2C%20you%20might%20think%20they%E2%80%99re%20bad%20because%20they%E2%80%99re%20fried%20in%20oil%20and%20salt%2C%20but%20they%20often%20contain%20many%20other%20additives%20that%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20realise%20or%20understand%2C%