h%20the%20show%2C%20we%20learn%20to%20embrace%20and%20accept%20ourselves.%20He%20has%20a%20message%20for%20every%20young%20person%20%E2%80%94%20whether%20they%20identify%20as%20male%2C%20female%2C%20or%20queer%3A%20%E2%80%9CMake%20money%2C%20but%20also%20make%20time%20for%20yourself.%20Be%20kind%20to%20yourself.%20All%20that%20matters%20is%20a%20good%20family%20and%20friend%20circle%2C%20and%20the%20creation%20of%20great%20memories.%20Maximise%20your%20time%20with%20your%20loved%20ones.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20one%20of%20my%20favourite%20episodes%20from%20the%20series%20%3Cem%3EBe%20A%20Man%2C%20Yaar%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20actor%20Imran%20Khan%20candidly%20shared%20his%20struggles%20with%20mental%20health.%20Discussing%20the%20stigma%20around%20therapy%2C%20he%20remarked%20how%20it%E2%80%99s%20often%20looked%20down%20upon%20to%20%E2%80%9Clie%20down%20on%20a%20couch%20and%20talk%20about%20feelings.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHow%20do%20you%20respect%20a%20man%20who%20is%20not%20earning%3F%20How%20do%20you%20respect%20a%20man%20who%20is%20not%20getting%20up%20and%20going%20to%20work%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20asked.%20It%E2%80%99s%20time%20we%20start%20respecting%20men%20who%20embrace%20their%20weaknesses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Arunava%20Banerjee%3B%20Images%20Courtesy%20Nikhil%20Taneja%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730126019000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-10-28-at-19.40.08-min-1730124705.jpeg%3Fw%3D1067%26quality%3D89%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D372684%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Nikhil%20Taneja%2C%20founder%20of%20Yuvaa%2C%20a%20youth%20media%20company%2C%20went%20through%20a%20period%20of%20great%20anxiety%20when%20he%20was%20doing%20well%20in%20his%20career.%20This%20led%20him%20to%20take%20a%20break%20and%20look%20at%20what%20success%20really%20means%2C%20breaking%20out%20of%20the%20d