ical%20conditions%2C%20respiratory%20concerns%2C%20skin%20and%20venereal%20diseases%2C%20ENT%20concerns%2C%20testing%2C%20treatment%20and%20counselling%20for%20tuberculosis%20and%20mental%20health%20concerns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20commitment%20to%20pioneer%20community%20health%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecognising%20that%20it%20is%20a%20privilege%20to%20be%20of%20service%20to%20those%20in%20the%20greatest%20need%2C%20Larsen%20%26amp%3B%20Toubro%20%E2%80%94%20a%20technology-led%20multinational%20that%20provides%20engineering%2C%20construction%2C%20manufacturing%2C%20and%20financial%20services%20%E2%80%94%20incepted%20the%20idea%20of%20community%20health%20centres.%20Today%2C%20these%20are%20staffed%20by%20expert%20doctors%2C%20nurses%2C%20and%20paramedics%20%E2%80%94%20keen%20on%20paying%20their%20dues%20back%20to%20society%20through%20their%20service.%20The%20therapeutic%20modalities%20are%20backed%20by%20excellent%20diagnostics%20and%20the%20latest%20technology%2C%20including%20X-rays%2C%20ultrasound%2C%20dental%20equipment%2C%20and%20equipment%20deployed%20in%20scopies.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Madhuri%20Franklin%2C%20who%20is%20at%20the%20helm%20of%20the%20operations%20at%20the%20Andheri%20centre%2C%20lets%20us%20in%20on%20the%20know-how%20of%20spearheading%20a%20project%20of%20this%20scope.%20The%20work%20is%20extensive%2C%20but%20she%20credits%20her%20drive%20to%20the%20satisfaction%20she%20derives%20from%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FxhChRC5wr8k%3Fsi%3DTa41NHAm0XHc6YMJ%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Dr%20Franklin%20whose%20professional%20trajectory%20has%20been%20coloured%20with%20experience%20in%20public%20health%20at%20the%20grassroots%20level%2C%20taking%20charge%20of%20this%2